    <item>
      <title>菲律宾前领导人杜特尔特在中国媒体上猛烈抨击美国和马科斯</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/ex-philippine-leader-duterte-slams-us-marcos-in-chinese-media</link>
      <description><![CDATA[前总统罗德里戈·杜特尔特指责美国加剧了中国和菲律宾在南海的紧张局势，同时批评他的继任者小费迪南德·马科斯据称听从美国的指挥。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/ex-philippine-leader-duterte-slams-us-marcos-in-chinese-media</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 04:39:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>意大利退出一带一路协议后，梅洛尼寻求中国重启</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/meloni-seeks-china-reset-after-italy-ditches-belt-and-road-pact</link>
      <description><![CDATA[意大利总理乔治亚·梅洛尼(Giorgia Meloni)在去年让意大利退出中国有争议的全球投资计划后，开始对北京发起魅力攻势，希望保护贸易和经济关系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/meloni-seeks-china-reset-after-italy-ditches-belt-and-road-pact</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 04:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登超越特朗普将中国实体列入黑名单的记录</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/biden-surpasses-trump-s-record-for-blacklisting-chinese-entities</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着世界最大经济体之间日益加剧的摩擦继续使全球贸易复杂化，美国总统乔·拜登将更多的中国企业和个人列入出口黑名单，数量比任何一届美国政府都多。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/biden-surpasses-trump-s-record-for-blacklisting-chinese-entities</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 03:30:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着防务关系的发展，美国计划在菲律宾进行芯片和镍交易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/us-plans-chips-nickel-deals-in-philippines-as-defense-ties-grow</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国计划支持菲律宾的基础设施、半导体和镍加工项目，因为这两个长期盟友在重新点燃防务关系后寻求发展投资伙伴关系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/us-plans-chips-nickel-deals-in-philippines-as-defense-ties-grow</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 03:12:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>秘鲁通过法案允许提取 70 亿美元养老金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/peru-passes-bill-allowing-for-7-billion-in-pension-withdrawals</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周四晚间，秘鲁国会以压倒性多数通过了一项法案，允许工人动用退休账户，当局估计这可能导致 70 亿美元的提款。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/peru-passes-bill-allowing-for-7-billion-in-pension-withdrawals</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 00:36:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>厄瓜多尔检察官办公室被要求对科雷亚叛国罪展开调查</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/ecuador-prosecutor-s-office-asked-to-open-correa-treason-probe</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据厄瓜多尔总统府的一份声明，厄瓜多尔检察官办公室被要求对前总统拉斐尔·科雷亚展开调查，罪名是他在与墨西哥的外交危机中发表的言论涉嫌叛国。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/ecuador-prosecutor-s-office-asked-to-open-correa-treason-probe</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 00:21:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新西兰和美国承诺在中国太平洋地区紧张局势中加强关系</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-11/new-zealand-us-pledge-closer-ties-amid-china-tension-in-pacific</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新西兰和美国承诺在共同挑战上进行更密切的合作，这进一步表明，随着中国在太平洋地区变得更加自信，惠灵顿正在与传统西方伙伴重新结盟。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-11/new-zealand-us-pledge-closer-ties-amid-china-tension-in-pacific</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Apr 2024 22:57:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>斯塔默承诺工党将维护英国的核威慑力量</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-11/starmer-promises-labour-will-preserve-uk-s-nuclear-deterrent</link>
      <description><![CDATA[基尔·斯塔默发誓，如果工党当选，工党将保留英国的核威慑力量，这突显出自取代杰里米·科尔宾成为党魁以来，他对反对党的改变有多大。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-11/starmer-promises-labour-will-preserve-uk-s-nuclear-deterrent</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Apr 2024 21:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着石油制裁最后期限临近，美国和委内瑞拉在墨西哥秘密会面</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-11/us-and-venezuela-secretly-meet-in-mexico-as-oil-sanctions-deadline-nears</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国官员本周与委内瑞拉总统尼古拉斯·马杜罗政府成员秘密会面，让他参与有关民主改革的谈判，因为恢复对该国石油工业制裁的最后期限已临近。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-11/us-and-venezuela-secretly-meet-in-mexico-as-oil-sanctions-deadline-nears</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Apr 2024 21:08:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登誓言支持日本和菲律宾，因为中国动摇了盟友</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-11/biden-vows-to-back-japan-philippines-as-china-rattles-allies</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统乔·拜登表示，他致力于“深化与日本和菲律宾的海上和安全关系”，因为他试图向担心中国在争议水域日益强硬行动的盟友保证。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-11/biden-vows-to-back-japan-philippines-as-china-rattles-allies</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Apr 2024 21:06:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
